Class Tstamp

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.tools.ant.ProjectComponent

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Tstamp
extends Task
    Sets properties to the current time, or offsets from the current time. The default properties are TSTAMP, DSTAMP and TODAY;
    Since:
    Ant 1.1
